            <p>Setup automation, Linear API integration, SQLite persistence, graceful shutdown, webhook tunneling.</p>
            <span class="roadmap-status">Complete</span>
          </div>
          <div class="roadmap-phase done">
            <h3>Phase B — Hardening</h3>
            <p>Structured logging, error audit, rate limiting, integration tests, company mode.</p>
            <span class="roadmap-status">Complete</span>
          </div>
          <div class="roadmap-phase current">
            <h3>Phase C — Intelligence</h3>
            <p>Cost tracking, performance metrics, smart alerts, self-healing CEO Office agent.</p>
            <span class="roadmap-status current-label">In Progress</span>
          </div>
          <div class="roadmap-phase">
            <h3>Phase D — Evolution</h3>
            <p>Multi-model runtime (Aider, Gemini CLI), dynamic roles, knowledge graph, prompt optimization.</p>
            <span class="roadmap-status">Planned</span>
          </div>
          <div class="roadmap-phase">
            <h3>Phase E — Product</h3>
            <p>Native macOS + iOS app, Docker deployment, CI/CD, plugin marketplace, multi-tenancy.</p>
            <span class="roadmap-status">Planned</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="docs-footer">
        <p>Can't find what you need? <a href="https://github.com/zzhiyuann/anc/issues">Open an issue</a> or check the <a href="https://github.com/zzhiyuann/anc">source code</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>

